* Iron Raptor turned a corner in one of the CFs many halls, she looked 
around, the past pain in her chest forgotten.
This was rather a big ship, one to easily get lost in, and she would be too 
if she wasn't careful.
She was just about to enter into a room on her right to explor when she 
heard Arcangles transmission, about bringing some bot in that had attacked 
them.
However, she didn't think that it needed a reasponse from her, her optics 
turning to the door she wanted to enter.
But then it happened again, that pain!
Iron Raptor didn't even know what hit her before she had her claws dug into 
the frame of the wall and hung there, her other hand clutched over ber spark 
and digging into her cybertronic flesh.
Sweat was already building up on her back and face, her optics wide at the 
pain.
All respitory functions had ceased as she cling there, before as ear 
splitting scream erupted from her throat and she fell to the floor!
Iron Raptor kneeled there, curling around herself until her forehead was 
touching her knees. Her optics clenched shut and her entire body trembling.
She screamed again, the pain not budging an inch.
Her shrill echoing through the halls both in front and behind her.
The Pain taking over.*
